versions.changeLog:
* Interim fix for GParted fails to run as root under Wayland;
* Fix reading Unicode labels when no FS specific tools available;
* Safely quote and escape external programs arguments;

* Printer couldn't be add;
* Replace icons deprecated by GTK 3.0 by non-deprecated ones;
* Improvements of discovered devices/connection type lists in new-printer wizard, more debug output; 
See details at https://github.com/zdohnal/system-config-printer/blob/1.5.11/NEWS

* Improved website rendering with the Retained Display List feature enabled;
* Fixed broken DevTools panels with certain extensions installed;
* Fixed a crash for users with some accessibility tools enabled.

* 优化了网站渲染，启用了保留显示列表功能;
* 安装了一些扩展程序修复损坏的DevTools面板;
* 修复了启用了某些辅助工具会导致崩溃的问题。

* VBoxManage: fixed MODIFYVM_AUDIOOUT;
* Serial: fixed possible data corruption when sending data under certain circumstances;
* Video recording: fixed starting / stopping recording under certain circumstances;
* Linux hosts: support Linux 4.17 changes;
* Linux guests: support Linux 4.16 and EL 7.5 kernels;
* Linux guests: 3D fixes for recent guests.

* Updated manual for deepin 15.7;
* Updated manual for Deepin File Manager;
* Updated manual for Deepin Graphics Driver Manager.

* Improved the recognition of bumblebee solution;

* Improved the dependent packages of prime solution;

* Improved error detection to reduce system crash;

* More detailed log files.

* Added power saving mode and auto mode switching function for laptops;
* Added mouse acceleration function;
* Fixed the notifications that were not shown;
* Optimized the scrolling in Control Center;
* Added application categories in Launcher mini mode;
* Supported using Tab key to jump between options;
* Fixed the issue that the login password cannot be input after waking the computer;
* Optimized the login animation;
* Other bug fixes.
To get more details, please visit https://www.deepin.org/release-notes/.

* Optimized the startup speed of the desktop;
* Fixed the position offset of wallpaper delete button when setting desktop wallpaper;
* Optimized the login process and background rendering;
* Launcher: Optimized mode switching and background rendering;
* Control Center: Optimized network modules and memory usage;
* Dock: Fixed the abnormal tooltip color in 2D mode; fixed the icon searching error; fixed the incorrect window preview position under HiDPI screen; optimized the hiding logic of wired network icon; added the default plugin order.

* Added auto index function; 
* Added permission management in properties; 
* Added support for renaming label of unmounted disk; 
* Added “Hide file extension when rename”in Settings; 
* Added support for changing tag orders; 
* Added support for changing column width in list view by dragging; 
* Added some prompts.

* Added auto index function;
* Added permission management in properties;
* Added support for renaming label of unmounted disk;
* Added “Hide file extension when rename”in Settings;
* Added support for changing tag orders;
* Added support for changing column width in list view by dragging;
* Added some prompts.

* Fixed the issue that files cannot be copied to sftp device directory;
* Fixed the issue that files in soft links were deleted after empty the trash on dock;
* Fixed the issue that blur image preview on HiDPI screen;
* Fixed auto mount failures.

* Fixed the wrong bookmark adding for folders in my shares;
* Fixed the incorrect content overwrite in smb;
* Fixed the issue that the files in folder are inaccessible after the folder permission was modified;
* Removed “Open with”and “Permission Management”in properties of file in trash.

* New tab options turned into gray when no more tabs can be opened;
* The space size of small capacity device was shown more accurately in Computer page;
* Fixed the issue that the file type of office documents were “Unknown” when WPS was not installed;
* Fixed the issue that the icon of connected phone was missing from the navigation bar under the dark theme;
* Fixed the incorrect svg (a format) preview in search results;
* Fixed the issue that Deepin File Manager or desktop environment crashes in some cases when dragging and dropping files;
* Fixed the incorrect “Open with” list for files in the archive preview.

* Added support for renaming the window title by OSC escape sequence;
* Fixed version number in About;
* Improved the judgment of monospaced fonts, and more monospaced fonts can be selected in the font list of settings;
* Fixed the issue that multiple menus appeared in some cases when right click continuously.
